اجين\n• يزيل التجاعيد والخطوط الدقيقة\n• يوحد لون البشرة\n• يقلل التصبغات.\n• لا يسبب الحساسية وتم اختباره على البشرة الحساسة','uploads/prod-3337875607254-1.jpg','uploads/prod-3337875607254-2.jpg','uploads/prod-3337875607254-g3.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875607254-g4.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875607254-g5.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875607254-g6.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875607254-g7.jpg\nuploads/prod-3337875607254-g8.jpg',1,0,0,8,'active','2026-07-13 19:28:06'),('vichy-liftactiv-collagen-specialist-eye-care-cre-73048','Vichy Liftactiv Collagen Specialist Eye Care Cream Anti-Ageing 15ml','Vichy','Skincare',37.98,NULL,NULL,'',0.0,0,20,5,'liftactiv','Targets Eye Ageing signs With Collagen Complex, Tested under dermatological and ophthalmological control, Suitable for sensitive eyes ,Tested on sensitive skin ,Fragrance-free','Liftactiv Collagen Specialist Eye Care cream, designed to help target the appearance of five eye ageing signs: crow’s feet, under eye wrinkles, eye bags, dark circles and drooping eye lids.\n\nAs we age, collagen production starts to decline, accelerating signs of skin ageing especially around the eyes. Formulated with a unique Pro-collagen Complex [Peptides + Pro-xylane + Vitamin C], this nourishing eye cream hydrates, brightens and smooths the eye area.\n\nRecommended by dermatologists, this eye cream is tested on sensitive skin and suitable for all skin types. Fragrance-free and subjected to ophthalmological control testing, it ensures both efficacy and safety for your delicate eye area.','3337875873048','322MB5874','15 ml','Apply twice a day after your serum\nGently massage into the eye contour','AQUA / WATER / EAU • GLYCERIN • DIMETHICONE • HYDROXYPROPYL TETRAHYDROPYRANTRIOL • ISONONYL ISONONANOATE • NIACINAMIDE • ALCOHOL DENAT. • CETYL ALCOHOL • GLYCERYL STEARATE • PEG-100 STEARATE • BUTYLENE GLYCOL • ASCORBYL GLUCOSIDE • BORON NITRIDE • PROPYLENE GLYCOL • DIMETHICONE/VINYL DIMETHICONE CROSSPOLYMER • AMMONIUM POLYACRYLOYLDIMETHYL TAURATE • STEARIC ACID • TRIET